Welcome to DragonSlayer


DragonSlayer is an initiative of the labict.be group and is meant as a project for students to collaborate on.


Goals
------
Learn students different aspects of web application development.
Learn students to collaborate on a single project.
Learn students to work with git.


Collaborating
--------------
More info on: https://help.github.com/articles/fork-a-repo
More info on: https://help.github.com/articles/using-pull-requests

~ Make sure to register an account on github.com.
~ Next fork the DragonSlayer project from https://github.com/BioBoost/DragonSlayer
~ Next clone your new forked repository from github "git clone https://github.com/<username>/DragonSlayer.git"
~ Next add an upstream remote pointing at the original forked repository "git remote add upstream https://github.com/BioBoost/DragonSlayer.git"
~ Fetch the upstream repository using "git fetch upstream"